title: BEAUTIFUL CORNER UNIT IN SLS BRICKELL!!
posting_body: ['Get to live on this LUXURY lifestyle CORNER 3Beds/2Baths/1HalfBaath condo with EXTRAORDINARY VIEWS from Biscayne Bay, Ocean and Miami Skyline.', 'Get to see the beautiful Miami SUNRISE and SUNSET everyday from the wrap-around balcony.', 'This unit has a spacious floor plan with lots of natural light with windows from floor to ceiling.', 'LUXURIOUS FINISHES and APPLIANCES in a Building that offers 5-STAR AMENITIES such as: 2 pools, Fitness Center, Billard, Theater Party Room and many more.', 'Excelente LOACATION in the heart of Brickell with walking distance to the best Restaurants, Shopping and Night Life.', 'This is a MUST SEE...!!!', 'all units are one year lease min!', 'credit score close to 700 or higher required, proof of income 2,5 greater than rent price, first month + last month + security deposit to move in!', 'Dilya Taveras', 'Equity Realty', 'TEXT :', 'show contact info']
